<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Ulang Tahun Bapak</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #000000, #111111);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
}

h1 {
    margin-top: 25px;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: #00ffd5;
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px #00ffd5;
}

p {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 15px;
}

.photo {
    margin: 20px auto;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 4px solid #ffd700;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ffd700;
    background: url('bapak.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
}

.gift {
    font-size: 120px;
    cursor: pointer;
    animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes bounce {
    0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
}

.motor {
    display: none;
    font-size: 120px;
    animation: zoom 1s ease;
}

@keyframes zoom {
    from { transform: scale(0); }
    to { transform: scale(1); }
}

.message {
    display: none;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin: 20px;
    color: #ffd700;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px #ffd700;
}

.heart {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: red;
    animation: float 4s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float {
    from { transform: translateY(100vh); opacity: 1; }
    to { transform: translateY(-10vh); opacity: 0; }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>ğŸ‰ Selamat Ulang Tahun, Bapak ğŸ‰</h1>

<div class="photo"></div>

<p>Terima kasih atas semua pengorbanan dan kasih sayangmu â¤ï¸</p>
<p><b>Klik hadiah di bawah ini ya Pak ğŸ˜Š</b></p>

<div class="gift" onclick="openGift()">ğŸ</div>

<div class="motor" id="motor">ğŸï¸</div>

<div class="message" id="message">
    ğŸ‰ Selamat ulang tahun, Bapak tercinta ğŸ‰<br><br>
    Ini hadiah dariku sebagai tanda terima kasih ğŸ’<br>
    Semoga motor ini selalu membawa Bapak dengan aman,<br>
    sehat, bahagia, dan penuh rezeki ğŸ¤²<br><br>
    Aku bangga punya Bapak sepertimu â¤ï¸
</div>

<audio id="music" src="ulangtahun.mp3"></audio>

<script>
function openGift() {
    document.querySelector('.gift').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('motor').style.display = 'block';
    document.getElementById('message').style.display = 'block';

    document.getElementById('music').play();
    createHearts();
}

function createHearts() {
    for (let i = 0; i < 35; i++) {
        let h = document.createElement('div');
        h.className = 'heart';
        h.innerHTML = 'â¤ï¸';
        h.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
        h.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 2 + 3) + 's';
        document.body.appendChild(h);
        setTimeout(() => h.remove(), 4000);
    }
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
